# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:4
translate chinese lisabreakfast_b90ab6dc:

    # "Lisa must have gone to work early. She didn't cook any breakfast. I guess she's still upset."
    "丽莎大概是早早去上班了。她没做早餐。我想她还在生气。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:12
translate chinese lisabreakfast_5ba2cbf3:

    # "Lisa stands in the kitchen, cooking some eggs in a pan on the stove."
    "丽莎站在厨房里，用平底锅在炉子上煎鸡蛋。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:19
translate chinese lisabreakfast_d41d8cd9:

    # voice 'voices/lisa_goodmorning.wav'
    voice 'voices/lisa_goodmorning.wav'

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:20
translate chinese lisabreakfast_09b21b2a:

    # sp "Good morning honey. Want some breakfast?"
    sp "早上好，亲爱的。要吃早餐吗？"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:35
translate chinese nottodaymom_d0417e78:

    # sp "Okay honey, let me know if you change your mind."
    sp "好的亲爱的，如果你改变主意了就告诉我。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:45
translate chinese lisabreakfastconvo_c299cac3:

    # sp "I'll cook you some eggs and bacon."
    sp "我给你做点鸡蛋和培根。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:46
translate chinese lisabreakfastconvo_e45e3b16:

    # "She returns to the stove and cooks us both breakfast."
    "她回到炉灶前，给我们俩做了早餐。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:49
translate chinese lisabreakfastconvo_2ccb9eb9:

    # "Then we sit down together and have a nice conversation while eating breakfast."
    "然后我们坐在一起，一边吃早餐一边愉快地聊天。"

# game/Scenes/Lisa/lisabreakfast.rpy:51
translate chinese lisabreakfastconvo_280140a3:

    # "Afterwards, she cleans up the plates and I head upstairs and get dressed for the day."
    "吃完后，她收拾了餐盘，我上楼换好衣服准备开始新的一天。"

